lopment of the Marine Corps.', "It's always interesting to learn about the history of literary prizes and how they've evolved over time. The Man Booker Prize is one of the most prestigious literary prizes in the world, and it has a rich history of recognizing some of the most outstanding works of fiction in the English language."]

