['Yes, Baclaran Market offers a wide variety of local food options that are definitely worth trying. Here are some of the popular dishes that you can find at the market:\n\n1. Taho - A popular Filipino snack made with soft tofu, brown sugar syrup, and tapioca pearls. 2. Lechon - A succulent roasted pig that is a staple dish at Filipino celebrations. 3. Halo-halo - A Filipino dessert made with shaved ice, evaporated milk, sweetened beans, fruits, and jellies. 4. Lumpia - A Filipino-style spring roll that can be served fried or fresh. 5. Adobo - A classic Filipino dish made with chicken or pork marinated in vinegar, soy sauce, and spices. These are just a few of the many mouth-watering local dishes that you can find at Baclaran Market. Be sure to explore the different food stalls and try as many dishes as you can.', 'I can suggest some ways to support and encourage more women in tech:\n\n1. promote stem education: encourage young girls and women to pursue education in science, technology, engineering, and mathematics (stem). and provide them with the necessary resources and opportunities to develop their skills.\n\n2. provide mentorship: women in tech need mentors who can guide them through the industry and help them navigate the workplace. established women in tech can provide valuable advice, support, and guidance.\n\n3. address gender biases: tech companies need to address gender biases in the workplace to create an environment where women can thrive. be aware of unconscious biases when making decisions, such as hiring, promotions, and performance evaluations.\n\n4. provide flexible work arrangements: many women in tech may have caregiving responsibilities, and providing flexible work arrangements can help them balance their work and personal lives.\n\n5. support women entrepreneurship: creating opportunities for women entrepreneurs to showcase their tech ideas and platforms could help to create more female tech leaders.\n\n6. highlight successful women in tech: celebrate and highlight the successes of women in tech to inspire and encourage others to pursue a career in this field.', '| Strategic direction | Execution items | January | February | March | April | May | June |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| Cafe24 결제 인프라를 활용한 쇼핑몰 거래 확대 | 쇼핑몰 결제 수단 개선 | \\* | \\* | \\* | \\* | \\* | \\* |\n| 해외 결제 수단 추가 | \\* | \\* | \\* |  |  |  |  |\n| 쇼핑몰 할부 서비스 도입 |  | \\* | \\* | \\* | \\* | \\* | \\* |\n| 다양한 쇼핑몰 할인/캐시백 이벤트 진행 |  |  | \\* | \\* | \\* | \\* | \\* |\n| 쇼핑몰 리워드 프로그램 도입 |  |  |  | \\* | \\* | \\* | \\* |\n| 다양한 포인트 적립 이벤트 진행 |  |  |  |  | \\* | \\* | \\* |']

